{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/nifty-npm-ntl","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b4aa9458-672c-5c15-b3d3-55bec15856aa","html":"<h3>How to install</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g ntl</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>cd into a folder containing <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> or you can point the project folder containing a <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> file and then enter the command</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ntl</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">Output</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"npm\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-npm line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-npm\">✔  Npm Task List - v3.2.1\n? Select a task to run: (Use arrow keys)\n❯ develop\n  build\n  format\n  start\n  serve\n  clean\n(Move up and down to reveal more choices)</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>When specifying a project folder, the <code class=\"language-text\">ntl</code> command takes an additional path parameter</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre sty